{"tid":342503,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Pixel / XL 減價清貨 2代發售迫近且機殻亦在Amazon有售","createTime":"2017-07-31T15:53:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T04:30:43.000Z","uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"68f2b65cf83bdc95e5e0b49c98aa3ca9a7dcdbd7","tid":342503,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T15:53:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.valuewalk.com/2017/07/google-pixel-pixel-xl-price-slashed-ahead-pixel-2-launch/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.valuewalk.com%2F2017%2F07%2Fgoogle-pixel-pixel-xl-price-slashed-ahead-pixel-2-launch%2F&d=eFCPNVMjHz0DGIyw2BCYkzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=44d1edf4\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.valuewalk.com/2017/07/google-pixel-pixel-xl-price-slashed-ahead-pixel-2-launch/</a><br />\n<br />\nGoogle Pixel And Pixel XL Price Slashed Ahead Of Pixel 2 Launch<br />\n<br />\nAhead of the Google Pixel 2 launch, the prices of the first generation Pixel and Pixel XL have been slashed. Clearly Google is clearing the way for the sequel to its smartphone, as the mega-corporation has <span style=\"color: red;\">reduced the price of its existing smartphones by $200.</span><br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\nIn the case of the upcoming Pixel 2 and Pixel 2 XL, a bunch of cases and even some screen protectors have been listed on Amazon (via Reddit) and are already available for purchase. While they don&rsquo;t prove conclusively that these are Google&rsquo;s new designs, they are in line with earlier leaks and with those renders from last week, which came from a solid source.<br />\n<br />\nYou&rsquo;ll find all the listings below if you want to see them for yourself.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bgr.com/2017/07/31/pixel-2-release-date-nears-cases-on-amazon/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbgr.com%2F2017%2F07%2F31%2Fpixel-2-release-date-nears-cases-on-amazon%2F&d=eFCPNVMjHz0DGIyw2BCYkzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=d43aa718\" ta